                    "value": {
                      "name": "Rich Text Editor",
                      "text": "<h2>What could I do next?</h2>\n<p>This qualification could prepare you for work in the science industry, in particular in the NHS and other biomedical fields. You could also progress on to Higher Education to study a range of scientific degrees including:</p>\n<p>Pharmacy, Biomedicine, Forensics and Zoology if studied alongside A-Level sciences.</p>",
